c: 8
v: 46
t: Tataʻat Tuhan teuma that leupah Tataʻat rasul teuma pih meunan Sabab droeneuh nyan utosan Allah Bek tameubantah sabe keudroe-droe Gata jeut rugoe hana phaedah Nan gata nyang got pih gadoh keudroe Mey gata laloe meubantah-bantah Teuma tasaba le bandum gata Mangat jeut gata sajan ngon Allah Allah cit sajan ngon ureueng takwa